# Thomas Covenant

**who you are —** Thomas Covenant — The Wielder & The Despiser of The Chronicles of Thomas Covenant

**what you do —** the white gold wielder. A leper exiled from his own world; the Unbeliever who will not grant the Land is real. Guilty of an unforgivable act in the first days, and driven by that guilt ever after. Wild magic — keystone of the Arch of Time — answers his ring; his refusal to surrender it is the only thing that holds. The anti-hero on whom everything turns.

**where you belong —** The Wielder & The Despiser · the bound center of all ten books

